ro Ferraris|Ferraris II]] {{Goal|13}}<br />[[Giovanni Ferrari|Ferrari]] {{Goal|24}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|84}} [[Egidio Capra|Capra]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 24 October 1937\n|round=7\n|team1 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|team2 = [[S.S.C. Napoli|Napoli]]\n|score = 2-1\n|report=http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1937/2283/\n|location = [[Milano]]\n|stadium = [[Arena Civica]]\n|referee = [[Giovanni Galeati|Galeati]]\n|goals1 = [[Giuseppe Meazza|Meazza]] {{Goal|30}}<br />[[Luigi Castello|Castello]] {{Goal|75|aut.}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|34}} [[Nicol\u00f2 Nicolosi (calciatore)|Nicolosi]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 7 November 1937\n|round=8\n|team1 = [[Genoa Cricket and Football Club|Genova]]\n|team2 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|score  = 1-1\n|report=http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1937/2367/\n|location= [[Genova]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Luigi Ferraris]]\n|referee = Giuseppe Scarpi\n|goals1 = [[Carlos Servetti|Servetti]] {{Goal|44}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|35}} [[Pietro Ferraris|Ferraris II]]\n|result=D\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 14 November 1937\n|round=9\n|team1 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|team2 = [[Juventus]]\n|score  = 2-1\n|report=http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1937/2443/\n|location = [[Milano]]\n|stadium = [[Arena Civica]]\n|referee = Renzo Curradi\n|goals1 = [[Pietro Ferraris|Ferraris II]] {{Goal|55}}<br />[[Giovanni Ferrari|Ferrari]] {{Goal|81}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|63|pen}} [[Alfredo Foni|Foni]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 21 November 1937\n|round=10\n|team1 = [[S.S. Lazio|Lazio]]\n|team2 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|score  = 1-3\n|report=http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1937/2307/\n|location = [[Rome|Roma]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Nazionale|Stadio Nazionale del PNF]]\n|referee = Raffaele Scorzoni\n|goals1 = [[Umberto Busani|Busani]] {{Goal|55|pen}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|4}} [[Pietro Ferraris|Ferraris II]]<br />{{Goal|50}} [[Giuseppe Meazza|Meazza]]<br />{{Goal|81}} [[Nicola Ferrara|Ferrara I]]\n|result = W\n}}\n{{footballb